cast.name: 保罗·斯科尔斯 Paul Scholes

this_title: Class of 92: Still Out of Their League Season 2
introduction: Last season, they reached the FA Cup second round for the first time in their history and were promoted to National League North, the sixth level of English football, the highest status they have ever achieved.Their average attendance was 642 for their 23 home league games. For the play-off final win against Workington they had a crowd of 1,967 at their Moor Lane ground.
